  ">",
  "> 各 transistor の平均損失は",
  "> $",
  "> P_{Q,\\text{each}}(\\hat V_O)",
  "> =",
  "> \\frac{V_{CC}\\hat V_O}{\\pi R_L}",
  "> -",
  "> \\frac{\\hat V_O^2}{4R_L}",
